metadata.name: Reign
metadata.description:
An eerie yet beautiful glimpse of what the World would look like when nature prevails over man-made landscapes. After over a millennium passes by, desert sand makes it way into Downtown, LA. 

Note for collectors:

• 3 ETH bid - Eligible for a signed fine art print
• 4 ETH bid - Eligible for an infinite objects
• 5 ETH bid - Eligible for both of the above

Music licensed for NFT use.
